name: Rocket Man Fly Endless
description:
Rocket Man Fly Endless!!!
Suit up with a Rocket Man and test your skills as legendary action hero
FEATURES:

* Fly the coolest jetpacks in gaming history
* Complete daring missions to boost your rank
* Customise your look with ridiculous outfits
* Dodge lasers, zappers, and guided missiles
* Collect coins and make boatloads of money
